<s> agreed, but my point is that the server's decision to enter into the reporting 'contract' and allow caching is a decision that is opaque to your proposal.  </s>
<s> There shouldn't be language that excludes some techniques because it isn't relevant or important, in a black-boxed decision we can't know what will be relevant.  </s>
